This directory contains Bluetooth driver layer code for BlueDroid stack.

WHAT IT DOES?
=============
It provides Bluetooth driver interfaces for stack usage.

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================

It needs the following libs from AOSP:
1. libcutils.so

and the following libs from MediaTek:
1. liblog.so
2. libnvram.so

All source/dependency modules of this module are already put in
'vendor/mediatek/libs' folder.


HOW TO USE IT?
==============

Files in this directory is used to
1. Generate a library named 'libbt-vendor.so' for BlueDroid stack.
2. Generate a library named 'libbluetooth_mtk.so', which provides the actual driver functions and linked by 'libbt-vendor.so'.


All the source code of this library were written by MediaTek co..

